column1: Baby Barnaby's////Based on all the reviews we tried this place for breakfast. It did not dissapoint at all. Priced well
column2: and a great amount of food. Very filling. We thought we were going to each get a course and split a waffle
column3: but Â neither one of us could finish our own plate
column4: so the waffle is to go. My only issue would be that you are shoulder to shoulder with others
column5: but for the food it's worth it.
